Detailed Description

cvmx_sli_msi_wr_map

This register is used to write the mapping function of the SLI_PCIE_MSI_RCV to SLI_MSI_RCV registers. At reset, the mapping function is one-to-one, that is MSI_INT 1 maps to CIU_INT 1, 2 to 2, 3 to 3, etc.
